.TH "SOURCEBUFFER.VIDEOTRACKS" "3JS" "October 31, 2025" "JavaScript" "JavaScript Reference Manual"
.SH NAME
SourceBuffer.videoTracks \- SourceBuffer: videoTracks property
.SH SYNOPSIS
\f[B]Note:\f[R] This feature is available in Dedicated Web Workers.
.PP
The \f[B]\f[CB]videoTracks\f[B]\f[R] read\-only property of the
\f[CR]SourceBuffer\f[R] interface returns a list of the video tracks
currently contained inside the \f[CR]SourceBuffer\f[R].
.SH VALUE
A \f[CR]VideoTrackList\f[R] object.
